                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021027-149-defend1283 t18021027-149-punish811"></join>
               Confined one month in Newgate
            </rs>, to <rs id="t18021027-149-punish812" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18021027-149-punish812" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18021027-149-punish812" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="pillory"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021027-149-defend1283 t18021027-149-punish812"></join>
               stand upon the pillory
            </rs>, and then to be <rs id="t18021027-149-punish813" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18021027-149-punish813" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021027-149-defend1283 t18021027-149-punish813"></join>
               transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
